revision.text:
{{Infobox cycling race report | name = 1934 Giro di Lombardia | date = October 21, 1934 | stages = 1 | distance = 245 | unit = km | first = [[Learco Guerra]] | first_nat = ITA | second = [[Mario Cipriani]] | second_nat = ITA | third = [[Domenico Piemontesi]] | third_nat = ITA | previous = [[1933 Giro di Lombardia|1933]] | next = [[1935 Giro di Lombardia|1935]] }} The '''1934 Giro di Lombardia''' was the 30th edition of the race. It was held on October 21, 1934, competing over a total route of 245 km. It was won by the Italian [[Learco Guerra]], reached the finish line with the time of 7h34 ' 00 "at an average of 32.378 km/h, preceding the countrymen [[Mario Cipriani]] and [[Domenico Piemontesi]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bikeraceinfo.com/classics/Tour%20of%20Lombardy/1934-giro-di-lombardia.html|title=1934 Giro di Lombardia results (Tour of Lombardy)|work=BikeRaceInfo|accessdate=5 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.memoire-du-cyclisme.net/cla_lombardie/lombardie1934.php|title=30ème Giro di Lombardia 1934|work=Memoire du cyclisme|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040126154210/http://www.memoire-du-cyclisme.net/cla_lombardie/lombardie1934.php|archivedate=26 January 2004}}</ref>
160 cyclists took off from Milan and 60 of them completed the race. ==General classification== {| |'''Final general classification'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.les-sports.info/cyclisme-sur-route-tour-de-lombardie-resultats-1934-epr10564.html|title=Tour de Lombardie 1934|work=LesSports.info|accessdate=4 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://firstcycling.com/race.php?r=24&y=1934|title=1934 Il Lombardia|work=First Cycling|accessdate=4 January 2018}}</ref> {| class="wikitable" |- ! scope="col" | Rank ! scope="col" | Rider ! scope="col" | Team ! scope="col" | Time |- |1 | {{flagathlete|[[Learco Guerra]]|ITA}} | [[Maino-Clement]] | 7h34 ' 00 " |- |2 | {{flagathlete|[[Mario Cipriani]]|ITA}} | [[Frejus]] | |- |3 | {{flagathlete|[[Domenico Piemontesi]]|ITA}} | [[Maino-Clement]] | |- |4 | {{flagathlete|[[Pietro Rimoldi]]|ITA}} | | |- |5 | {{flagathlete|[[René Vietto]]|FRA}} | | |- |6 | {{flagathlete|[[Francesco Camusso]]|ITA}} | [[Gloria (cycling team)|Gloria]] | |- |7 | {{flagathlete|[[Remo Scorticati]]|ITA}} | | |- |8 | {{flagathlete|[[Severino Canavesi]]|ITA}} | [[Legnano-Wolsit]] | |- |9 | {{flagathlete|[[Giovanni Cazzulani]]|ITA}} | [[Gloria (cycling team)|Gloria]] | |- |10 | {{flagathlete|[[Edoardo Molinar]]|ITA}} | | |} |}
