'''Anaji'''<ref>[http://www.maplandia.com/ghana/western/sekondi-takoradi/anaji/ Anaji - Maplandia]</ref> is a town in the [[Western Region, Ghana|Western region]] of [[Ghana]]. It is 10 kilometres from the centre [[Takoradi]], the Western regional [[Sekondi-Takoradi|capital]].
==Boundaries== The village is bordered on the north by Namibia (a suburb of Takoradi), to the West by [[Kansaworodo]], to the east by [[Nkroful]] and to the South by [[Effiakuma]].
