{{Infobox Airport | name = Séguéla Airport | nativename = {{lang|fr|Aéroport de Séguéla}} | image = | image-width = | caption = | IATA = SEO | ICAO = DISG | type = Public | owner = | operator = | city-served = [[Séguéla]], Côte d'Ivoire | location = | coordinates = {{coord|7|57|36|N|006|38|39|W|region:CI|display=inline,title}} | pushpin_map = Côte d'Ivoire | pushpin_label = '''SEO''' | pushpin_map_caption = Location in Côte d'Ivoire | elevation-f = 1,056 | elevation-m = 322 | website = | metric-elev = y | metric-rwy = y | r1-number = ? | r1-length-f = 6,398 | r1-length-m = 1,950 | r1-surface = ? | stat-year = | stat1-header = | stat1-data = | stat2-header = | stat2-data = | footnotes = }}
'''Séguéla Airport''' ({{lang-fr|Aéroport de Séguéla}}) {{airport codes|SEO|DISG}} is an [[airport]] serving [[Séguéla]], a town in Côte d'Ivoire. It is located about {{convert|3|km}} to the east of the town. The airport has one runway measuring {{convert|1950|m}} that will be asphalted.
==Infrastructure== Séguéla Airport has one runway with dimensions {{convert|1950|x|40|m}}.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.gcmap.com/airport/SEO | title=SEO - Séguéla [Séguéla Airport], 14, CI - Airport | work=Great Circle Mapper | accessdate=19 November 2016}}</ref> During a July 2015 press conference in Séguéla, President [[Alassane Ouattara]] said that the runway would be asphalted by 2020 at a cost of 7 billion [[West African CFA franc]]s.<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.lebabi.net/actualite-abidjan/le-chef-de-l-etat-a-anime-769-un-giga-meeting-a-768-se-769-gue-769-la-dans-le-cadre-de-sa-visite-d-etat-dans-le-district-du-woroba-51545.html | title=Le Chef de l’Etat a animé un giga-meeting à Séguéla dans le cadre de sa visite d’Etat dans le District du Woroba | work=Lebabi.net | date=27 July 2015 | accessdate=19 November 2016 | language=French}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.gouv.ci/_actualite-article.php?recordID=5857&d=1 | title=Au terme de sa tournee dans le Woroba, le Chef de l'Etat a echange avec la presse | work=Official portal of the government of Côte d'Ivoire | date=26 July 2015 | accessdate=19 November 2016 | language=French}}</ref>
